{
  "stem": "3666.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't just-- it was an interesting day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to tell you the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least I think it was on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father decided that he would take myself and my brother on a boat ride.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Vilna had water, surrounded by water, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a river.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used to have boats there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he decided that he would take my brother and myself on that day on an excursion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother did not come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I still remember walking the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were-- I don't know how we got there, either by bus or I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we never got to really to the boat, to the marina, but we were en route to the marina.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And suddenly, people started to run in the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people were running into gates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, when I say gates, I mean that most buildings had a gate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you entered the gate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's like sort of European style.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were running into the gates, off the streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And nobody knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My, my father didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And suddenly we began to hear bombs coming down, like rain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And of course, then my father asked around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was speaking to people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And within the hour, we knew that there was an invasion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't even know exactly who, at least I didn't [LAUGHS] really know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe my father did, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course we never made it to the-- to the boat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And we knew by then that we are in, in great trouble, especially the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because the Jews knew what the Germans are going to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
